		"description": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-02761f40-7fff-2e77-428c-a18a206f644d\" dir=\"ltr\">When you reach 6th level, you gain a bonus adaptation&ndash;one showing how your closeness with elemental energy has begun to affect your mind and emotions. Choose one adaptation from the following list: Burning Fury, Courts of the Elemental Lords, Earthsense, Ebb and Flow, Elemental Performance, Elemental Transmission, Fire&rsquo;s Warmth, Stone&rsquo;s Composure, Veil of Mists, Voice of the Wind, and Greater Voice of the Wind.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You gain another bonus invocation in this way at 14th level. When you gain a level in this class, you can choose one of the bonus infocations you know and replace it with another bonus invocation from this list that you could learn at that level.</p>",
